!v704!<p><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica-Normal, sans-serif" size="3"><b>ANVISA    LAN&Ccedil;A SISTEMA PARA APRIMORAR CONTROLE DE INFEC&Ccedil;&Atilde;O HOSPITALAR</b></font></p>     ^cY
!v705!S
!v706!p
!v708!69
!v709!text
!v880!S0034-89102004000100023
!v882!^v38^n1
!v936!^i0034-8910^y2004^o1
